          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontname='Times New Roman'>Impact of Supply Shocks on Market Concentration (ΔHHI)</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='9'>Change in concentration under disruption scenarios; negative values indicate diversification, positive values indicate increased concentration</run>
